  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You imitate the aether-draining effect of a vampire bat's bite, drawing the life force from a creature whilst replenishing your own. The target takes 2d4 shadow damage, and must make a Fortitude save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes half damage.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes normal damage, and you gain 1 temporary hit point.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target takes double damage and you gain 2 temporary hit points.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The damage increases by 1d4, and the temporary hit points gained increase by 1, or 2 on a critical failure.</p>"
